## Examples

Examining values

```
gosh -e 'ctx := context.WithValue(context.Background(), "K", 42)' \
     -e 'pretty.Println(ctx)'
```

: Note that the 'pretty' package is not in the standard library
: It uses github.com/kr/pretty

