## Examples

Quickly exploring Go library behaviour

<br>

```
gosh -e 'fmt.Printf("%+4.9X\n", 42)'
gosh -pf '"%+4.9X\n", 42'
gosh -pf '"%+9.4X\n", 42'
gosh -pf '"%+9.3X\n", 42'
gosh -pf '"%+9X\n", 42'
gosh -pf '"%+9x\n", 42'
gosh -pf '"%+9o\n", 42'
```

